<h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>1. What is the Social Media Marketplace?</h2>
        <p>The Social Media Marketplace is a secure platform that allows users to communicate through encrypted messaging, share media securely, and participate in a peer-to-peer marketplace.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>2. How is my data secured?</h2>
        <p>We use end-to-end encryption for messaging and media sharing. All communication is secured with HTTPS/TLS, and we never store plain-text passwords.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>3. How do I verify my account?</h2>
        <p>During registration, you must verify your email and mobile number through an OTP-based authentication system.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>4. How do I report suspicious activity?</h2>
        <p>You can report users or content by using the "Report" feature available on user profiles and messages. Our admin team will review all reports and take necessary action.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>5. Is my payment information safe?</h2>
        <p>Yes, we do not store credit card details. Payments are processed securely through third-party payment gateways using tokenized transactions.</p>
    </div>

